    <title>Availability and requirements</title>
    <p id="Par25">Project name: gcMECM; Project home page: <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://github.com/CBIIT-CGBB/gcMECM">https://github.com/CBIIT-CGBB/gcMECM</ext-link>; Operating system(s): Platform independent; Programming language: R; Other requirements: R (&gt; = 3.5), igraph, Rtsne; License: GNU GPL v2.0; Any restrictions to use by non-academics: No.</p>
  </sec>
